11
00:01:37.981 --> 00:01:39.451
But let's...

12
00:01:39.951 --> 00:01:41.012
- try... - No.

13
00:01:42.951 --> 00:01:44.481
No, wait.

14
00:01:44.481 --> 00:01:45.692
Wait. No, Ha Ri...

15
00:01:45.692 --> 00:01:46.822
Ha Ri.

16
00:01:47.852 --> 00:01:48.921
Wait.

17
00:03:04.162 --> 00:03:08.141
(Episode 11: No Words Can Express...)

18
00:03:08.141 --> 00:03:12.141
