46
00:04:45.972 --> 00:04:47.931
Okay, fine. Sure.

47
00:04:49.241 --> 00:04:51.302
- Really? - Yes.

48
00:04:56.141 --> 00:04:58.982
- Any parcels for "The Baby"? - Just a second.

49
00:05:11.362 --> 00:05:12.831
Thank you.

50
00:05:20.072 --> 00:05:21.132
Hello.

51
00:05:25.372 --> 00:05:27.541
Don't you have anything to say to me?

52
00:05:32.711 --> 00:05:34.351
I mean...

53
00:05:35.622 --> 00:05:36.822
Well...

54
00:05:42.461 --> 00:05:43.891
They are too heavy.

55
00:05:54.872 --> 00:05:56.341
Why did you do that?

56
00:05:56.942 --> 00:05:58.211
What?

57
00:05:58.841 --> 00:06:02.141
Did something happen during the weekend?

58
