Is she the person you wanted to ask out?

62
00:07:20.021 --> 00:07:22.291
Eu Ddeum, please organize this.

63
00:08:14.512 --> 00:08:15.812
How is Do Ah?

64
00:08:16.341 --> 00:08:18.242
She took medicine, so she'll be fine.

65
00:08:28.461 --> 00:08:30.692
She really should clean this up.

66
00:08:30.692 --> 00:08:32.562
She'll get hurt on her way down.

67
00:08:40.502 --> 00:08:42.771
You should go upstairs. I think she came home.

68
00:08:46.141 --> 00:08:47.841
I have nothing to say to her.

69
00:08:52.012 --> 00:08:54.081
Why? Can't you even look at her?

70
00:08:58.591 --> 00:09:00.391
I'm scared I might confess my feelings.

71
00:09:00.922 --> 00:09:02.362
Then it'll end our relationship.

72
00:09:06.832 --> 00:09:09.061
I totally approve of you.

73
00:09:10.102 --> 00:09:13.132
It's too bad that Ha Ri doesn't feel the same way.

74
00:09:17.141 --> 00:09:19.311
Why do you approve of me being with her though?

75
00:09:19.811 --> 00:09:21.271
I'm a divorced single father.

76
00:09:21.612 --> 00:09:23.342
I'm a divorced single mother too.

77
00:09:28.051 --> 00:09:30.821
To Ha Ri, you were like...

78
00:09:30.821 --> 00:09:32.952
a father and a brother.

79
00:09:34.252 --> 00:09:35.992
I felt bad that she was always alone,

80
00:09:36.362 --> 00:09:39.061
so I was glad to know that she at least had you.

81
00:09:39.632 --> 00:09:42.531
It's why I depended on you too.

82
00:09:46.472 --> 00:09:49.202
Decades ago, your mom and I...

83
00:09:50.071 --> 00:09:52.171
promised to have our kids marry each other,

84
00:09:52.472 --> 00:09:54.472
but you went chasing after another girl.

85
00:09:59.982 --> 00:10:02.821
The man Ha Ri's seeing...

86
00:10:03.622 --> 00:10:06.252
Is he the one she went to Mureung with?

87
00:10:08.821 --> 00:10:09.921
Yes.

88
00:10:10.122 --> 00:10:11.931
Is he not up to par?

89
00:10:12.691 --> 00:10:13.791
Won't it work out?

90
00:10:16.161 --> 00:10:17.962
Are you waiting because they'll break up?

91
00:10:25.311 --> 00:10:27.612
Truth be told, I don't want her to be with anyone.

92
00:10:30.512 --> 00:10:34.352
But what can I do when he's the one...

93
00:10:35.821 --> 00:10:38.051
Ha Ri truly wants?

94
00:10:39.752 --> 00:10:40.921
I should give up.

95
00:10:46.061 --> 00:10:47.061
Gosh.

96
00:10:49.002 --> 00:10:50.632
Goodness, Do Ah.

97
00:11:04.612 --> 00:11:06.582
So did you two break up?

98
00:11:07.112 --> 00:11:08.212
Is that it?

99
00:11:09.722 --> 00:11:12.891
Are we supposed to do this until your heart heals from the pain?

100
00:11:13.791 --> 00:11:14.891
Is that it?

101
00:11:16.222 --> 00:11:17.391
We won't break up.

102
00:11:18.222 --> 00:11:19.291
Then tell me.

103
00:11:21.931 --> 00:11:24.862
Why did you make me come here at this hour...

104
00:11:24.862 --> 00:11:26.771
when you and Ms. Jang are still solid?

105
00:11:31.801 --> 00:11:32.872
What the...

106
00:11:34.911 --> 00:11:36.541
- Darn it. - I'm infertile.

107
00:11:41.452 --> 00:11:43.921
- What? - Why did I find it hard to say...

108
00:11:44.482 --> 00:11:45.592
when it's this easy?

109
00:11:47.592 --> 00:11:48.622
You?

110
00:11:49.691 --> 00:11:51.592
You and not Ms. Jang?

111
00:11:53.291 --> 00:11:56.362
I Sang, is that why you and In Ah broke up?

112
00:11:56.762 --> 00:11:59.502
So? Does Ms. Jang want to end things too?

113
00:12:05.071 --> 00:12:06.842
It only had to be hard for me,

114
00:12:07.911 --> 00:12:09.012
but now...

115
00:12:18.321 --> 00:12:19.391
Soo Chul.

116
00:12:20.992 --> 00:12:22.421
There's somewhere I need to go.

117
00:12:23.191 --> 00:12:24.291
Go ahead without me.

118
00:13:57.072 --> 00:13:58.213
I'm sorry.

119
00:14:00.812 --> 00:14:01.912
I'm truly sorry.

120
00:14:03.583 --> 00:14:04.682
What I did...

121
00:14:07.083 --> 00:14:08.253
was wrong.

122
00:14:12.052 --> 00:14:13.123
I just...

123
00:14:14.662 --> 00:14:15.932
wanted to tell you that.

124
00:14:21.633 --> 00:14:23.072
Tell me...

125
00:14:24.003 --> 00:14:25.103
the rest of your story.

126
00:14:43.853 --> 00:14:45.152
Before the wedding,

127
00:14:48.393 --> 00:14:50.093
I got myself tested.

128
00:14:53.562 --> 00:14:54.932
I didn't show any symptoms...

129
00:14:56.702 --> 00:14:58.302
and everything seemed normal,

130
00:15:01.473 --> 00:15:04.013
so I didn't think there would be an issue.

131
00:15:07.343 --> 00:15:11.182
But we found out that I had a fertility issue.

132
00:15:12.083 --> 00:15:14.123
We thought that I'd get better...

133
00:15:14.822 --> 00:15:17.253
after three months of treatment,

134
00:15:19.593 --> 00:15:20.893
but only a painful breakup...

135
00:15:23.032 --> 00:15:24.093
awaited us.

136
00:15:28.532 --> 00:15:29.603
My heart...

137
00:15:31.973 --> 00:15:33.343
went through...

138
00:15:34.702 --> 00:15:36.113
the most painful time...

139
00:15:37.772 --> 00:15:39.442
moving on from that breakup...

140
00:15:42.753 --> 00:15:44.013
that I didn't want...

141
00:15:47.422 --> 00:15:50.952
to get involved with you because it could lead to a similar outcome.

142
00:15:55.522 --> 00:15:56.662
However,

143
00:16:00.302 --> 00:16:01.963
I fell for you,

144
00:16:03.572 --> 00:16:04.733
and I knew...

145
00:16:07.572 --> 00:16:08.843
that my condition...

146
00:16:11.312 --> 00:16:12.782
would hurt you more...

147
00:16:17.182 --> 00:16:18.312
which is what...

148
00:16:20.452 --> 00:16:21.822
worried me the most.

149
00:16:26.723 --> 00:16:27.922
You also...

150
00:16:31.263 --> 00:16:34.503
experienced your world ending in front of your eyes.

151
00:16:41.502 --> 00:16:44.873
Still, if you didn't want to hurt me...

152
00:16:46.343 --> 00:16:47.843
and if you cared about me,

153
00:16:50.383 --> 00:16:52.182
you should've told me sooner.

154
00:16:57.492 --> 00:16:59.962
Accepting my own fate was hard enough.

155
00:17:06.702 --> 00:17:07.803
I should go.

156
00:17:51.543 --> 00:17:53.742
She never bothered to drink these,

157
00:17:54.212 --> 00:17:56.383
but I see that she has been this time.

158
00:18:24.543 --> 00:18:26.813
Okay, take a deep breath.

159
00:18:27.182 --> 00:18:28.343
And exhale.

160
00:18:28.543 --> 00:18:29.712
All done.

161
00:18:30.652 --> 00:18:32.952
The pneumonia is lasting longer than I expected.

162
00:18:33.283 --> 00:18:34.452
That's bad, isn't it?

163
00:18:34.452 --> 00:18:37.492
It'll get better once we treat it, so don't worry.

164
00:18:37.952 --> 00:18:39.863
Are you having fun? Here.

165
00:18:40.262 --> 00:18:43.363
I'll buy you ice cream once you're all better. I promise.

166
00:18:46.563 --> 00:18:48.502
- You're free to go. - Thank you.

167
00:18:49.502 --> 00:18:50.873
Doctor.

168
00:18:51.432 --> 00:18:54.043
- Thank you. - Goodbye.

169
00:19:21.502 --> 00:19:23.472
What do luxurious baby panties...

170
00:19:23.472 --> 00:19:26.202
and elegant bloomers look like?

171
00:19:26.303 --> 00:19:28.873
They look luxurious and elegant.

172
00:19:29.273 --> 00:19:32.172
Hyo Joo. Can you not write an article...

173
00:19:32.172 --> 00:19:33.583
without using slang?

174
00:19:33.982 --> 00:19:36.883
- Rewrite it without slang. - Yes, ma'am.

175
00:19:40.752 --> 00:19:43.222
- What? - The baby model can't make it...

176
00:19:43.523 --> 00:19:45.692
for the toy ad. They called and notified us.

177
00:19:45.893 --> 00:19:47.793
Please bring your friend's baby.

178
00:19:48.593 --> 00:19:51.262
You sound so arrogant, I feel like I owe you.

179
00:19:51.762 --> 00:19:52.803
Fine.

