00:20:00.643 --> 00:20:02.543
(List of ovulation-inducing agents)

181
00:20:04.543 --> 00:20:07.242
(List of ovulation-inducing agents)

182
00:20:14.353 --> 00:20:16.053
- Yeon Ho. - Yes?

183
00:20:16.793 --> 00:20:19.053
Do men get injections of ovulation agents too?

184
00:20:19.462 --> 00:20:22.863
Yes. They use that to treat male infertility too.

185
00:20:22.863 --> 00:20:24.492
I hear men have to get it...

186
00:20:24.492 --> 00:20:26.502
2 to 3 times a week for 3 months straight.

187
00:20:28.202 --> 00:20:32.103
I knew it was hard on women, but it must be hard on men too.

188
00:20:54.992 --> 00:20:56.063
What?

189
00:20:56.662 --> 00:20:59.502
I'm really going to change jobs this time.

190
00:21:00.732 --> 00:21:03.232
You said you were really going to change jobs last time too.

191
00:21:03.533 --> 00:21:07.103
You're not a pathological liar, are you?

192
00:21:07.103 --> 00:21:09.143
You brat. I mean it.

193
00:21:12.712 --> 00:21:14.712
I have no reason to stay here anymore.

194
00:21:15.113 --> 00:21:18.353
But one year doesn't even count as experience, right?

195
00:21:18.353 --> 00:21:20.823
Is it better to switch jobs after 1 to 2 years,

196
00:21:20.823 --> 00:21:21.883
or...

197
00:21:21.952 --> 00:21:24.922
is it better to find a new job as quickly as possible?

198
00:21:25.353 --> 00:21:28.162
If you get hired for the job you want, you take it. Period.

199
00:21:30.293 --> 00:21:32.762
This was the job I wanted.

200
00:21:35.232 --> 00:21:36.502
Oh my gosh.

201
00:21:39.672 --> 00:21:43.343
Why are you whispering instead of doing your work?

202
00:21:44.442 --> 00:21:45.573
Include me too.

203
00:21:48.583 --> 00:21:50.752
Competitors keep shutting down,

204
00:21:51.083 --> 00:21:53.652
so people keep calling to ask if we'll have an issue next month.

205
00:21:53.682 --> 00:21:56.152
I guess I should find a new job.

206
00:21:57.853 --> 00:21:59.462
I feel your pain.

207
00:22:00.422 --> 00:22:03.633
They say that every year. I'm sure it's just a rumor.

208
00:22:03.762 --> 00:22:06.202
I don't think it is, that's why.

209
00:22:35.023 --> 00:22:36.492
Why are you...

210
00:22:39.833 --> 00:22:41.133
What are you doing here...

211
00:22:43.873 --> 00:22:46.002
It's working hours.

212
00:22:48.672 --> 00:22:49.773
So?

213
00:23:04.023 --> 00:23:05.123
Are you hurt?

214
00:23:06.722 --> 00:23:08.162
Why do you care?

215
00:23:08.523 --> 00:23:10.893
What's it to you even if I break my wrist?

216
00:23:13.333 --> 00:23:14.462
Because I know you personally.

217
00:23:21.702 --> 00:23:25.012
Do you care about and take care of everyone woman you know?

218
00:23:25.543 --> 00:23:28.742
You're a real jerk, you know that?

219
00:23:30.652 --> 00:23:33.383
I know I may be a bit dumb, but I'm not a bad person.

220
00:23:33.383 --> 00:23:34.652
Listen.

221
00:23:35.283 --> 00:23:37.192
You don't know you're bad, right?

222
00:23:37.893 --> 00:23:39.293
That's even worse.

223
00:23:43.533 --> 00:23:45.063
Why are you being like this to me?

224
00:23:45.492 --> 00:23:47.103
Why am I a bad person?

225
00:23:47.633 --> 00:23:50.672
What bad things did I do to you? I don't understand.

226
00:23:54.873 --> 00:23:56.442
Why are you considerate?

227
00:23:58.512 --> 00:24:00.843
Why did you run to the store to buy me bandage,

228
00:24:01.442 --> 00:24:02.813
smile at me,

229
00:24:03.912 --> 00:24:05.682
and make me get the wrong idea?

230
00:24:09.083 --> 00:24:11.053
I'm so humiliated.

231
00:24:19.293 --> 00:24:21.962
- Why are you crying? - I'm not crying.

232
00:24:27.843 --> 00:24:30.012
Why is this running?

233
00:24:30.113 --> 00:24:32.813
This was supposed to be waterproof.

234
00:24:32.813 --> 00:24:34.543
Are you crying because your mascara ran?

235
00:24:34.883 --> 00:24:37.512
I'll buy you a better one, so don't cry.

236
00:24:37.512 --> 00:24:38.783
Hey!

237
00:24:38.783 --> 00:24:41.523
Stop that, will you?

238
00:24:41.853 --> 00:24:45.222
Don't be so nice to me.

239
00:24:50.932 --> 00:24:52.932
Do you sell mascara here?

240
00:25:12.452 --> 00:25:15.853
Are you unable to go in because of me?

241
00:25:44.512 --> 00:25:45.783
A test shot.

242
00:25:47.283 --> 00:25:49.152
We'll use a small picture as an image cut.

243
00:26:02.633 --> 00:26:03.702
Like this?

244
00:26:04.002 --> 00:26:05.402
That's good. Yes.

245
00:26:10.543 --> 00:26:13.242
- I'll help you. - No, I'll do it.

246
00:26:27.563 --> 00:26:28.762
I said...

247
00:26:30.033 --> 00:26:31.863
I was afraid of hurting you, right?

248
00:26:33.603 --> 00:26:35.762
So I won't.

249
00:26:37.333 --> 00:26:40.873
Let's find a way together.

250
00:26:42.472 --> 00:26:46.073
I'll do everything I can,

251
00:26:46.543 --> 00:26:49.442
- so... - You said it was unbearably hard.

252
00:26:51.682 --> 00:26:53.623
You said it came to a painful end.

253
00:27:00.393 --> 00:27:02.492
You said love is like a miracle.

254
00:27:03.732 --> 00:27:06.502
You said you never let go of the people you love.

255
00:27:06.962 --> 00:27:09.202
That's the solution I'm thinking of.

256
00:27:14.773 --> 00:27:17.442
It'll kill you inside because you can't give it to me.

257
00:27:19.242 --> 00:27:21.543
And it'll kill me inside because I can't be hopeful.

258
00:27:23.182 --> 00:27:26.383
We'd be perfectly fine if we didn't want kids.

259
00:27:28.482 --> 00:27:30.023
If it weren't for me,

260
00:27:30.853 --> 00:27:33.523
you wouldn't have to suffer this pain.

261
00:27:33.563 --> 00:27:35.262
Don't say that, Ha Ri.

262
00:27:37.633 --> 00:27:39.462
Maybe we never should've started to begin with.

263
00:28:03.692 --> 00:28:05.593
- Did you go to Art Department? - Yes.

264
00:28:07.123 --> 00:28:08.123
Where's Ms. Jang?

265
00:28:08.422 --> 00:28:10.932
- Did she go somewhere? - Yes.

266
00:28:11.432 --> 00:28:15.133
By the way, Hyo Joo disappeared.

267
00:28:16.002 --> 00:28:17.073
She disappeared?

268
00:28:17.603 --> 00:28:20.073
Her bag is still here, but she was gone all day,

269
00:28:20.073 --> 00:28:21.343
and I can't even reach her.

270
00:28:21.643 --> 00:28:24.742
Do you think she drank during working hours again?

271
00:28:24.912 --> 00:28:26.783
- No! - Gosh, you startled me.

272
00:28:28.712 --> 00:28:31.012
She helped me organize the storage room today.

