368
00:35:52.060 --> 00:35:53.161
Okay.

369
00:35:53.661 --> 00:35:56.460
Let's wait and see how things turn out for you.

370
00:35:56.630 --> 00:36:00.040
Sure. You can sit back and watch...

371
00:36:00.940 --> 00:36:02.601
