393
00:38:43.770 --> 00:38:45.101
We learn leather crafting together.

394
00:38:45.201 --> 00:38:46.270
"We"?

395
00:38:46.900 --> 00:38:48.071
Together?

396
00:38:48.900 --> 00:38:52.210
I meant that we take the same classes.

397
00:38:52.610 --> 00:38:53.681
