399
00:39:04.020 --> 00:39:08.391
Didn't you call me your son-in-law just now?

400
00:39:09.121 --> 00:39:10.130
What?

401
00:39:10.290 --> 00:39:12.230
Son-in-law?

402
00:39:12.690 --> 00:39:13.761
What?

403
00:39:16.931 --> 00:39:19.871
Anyway, Ha Ri went to the office early,

404
00:39:19.871 --> 00:39:22.270
so you should head to work too.

405
00:39:22.900 --> 00:39:24.670
