00:39:43.290 --> 00:39:46.790
Ha Ri's mother called me her son-in-law earlier.

409
00:39:49.261 --> 00:39:51.931
- Forget it. - She approved of me...

410
00:39:52.670 --> 00:39:54.201
a long time ago.

411
00:39:54.571 --> 00:39:55.871
We should head to work.

412
00:39:56.141 --> 00:39:57.940
That's exactly what I'm doing.

413
00:40:25.571 --> 00:40:26.670
It's Jeon Tae Hui.

414
00:40:27.770 --> 00:40:29.071
I've never seen a celebrity before.

415
00:40:29.071 --> 00:40:32.071
