443
00:41:46.451 --> 00:41:47.650
Gosh!

444
00:41:47.980 --> 00:41:49.551
- Let's go. - Hold on.

445
00:41:49.980 --> 00:41:51.451
Do you have a photo shoot today?

446
00:41:53.090 --> 00:41:56.460
