447
00:42:03.431 --> 00:42:06.101
Ms. Jang, you should get over there.

448
00:42:07.170 --> 00:42:09.540
- Why? - To book Jeon Tae Hui.

449
00:42:11.040 --> 00:42:12.110
Me?

450
00:42:12.911 --> 00:42:15.511
Good. That's great.

451
00:42:16.210 --> 00:42:18.681
All right. That looks amazing.

452
00:42:19.710 --> 00:42:22.081
