487
00:44:28.581 --> 00:44:30.551
Most of them end up making things up.

488
00:44:34.851 --> 00:44:37.391
What if we became well-acquainted then?

489
00:44:37.391 --> 00:44:38.951
I'll give you some space.

490
00:44:40.051 --> 00:44:42.821
