528
00:47:28.560 --> 00:47:31.290
Is there a reason other than the fact that I have a kid?

529
00:47:34.860 --> 00:47:38.331
I know you were willing to say anything to keep Jeong Won,

530
00:47:38.471 --> 00:47:39.770
but was that necessary?

531
00:47:41.371 --> 00:47:42.500
What?

532
00:47:45.411 --> 00:47:49.241
I hate you for not even knowing...

533
00:47:49.641 --> 00:47:50.980
that you hurt her.

534
00:48:04.290 --> 00:48:05.360
Hello?

535
00:48:05.960 --> 00:48:07.931
- Are you on your way? - Yes.

536
00:48:08.301 --> 00:48:09.761
